Plugins.unlink

機能/意味
Detach plugin
タイプ
Pluginsクラスのメソッド
構文
unlink(name)
引数
name 　Specify the plug-in to be detached.
戻り値
　True if successful, false if unsuccessful
説明
　Detach the specified plug-in.
　Some plug-ins do not respond to release (for example, when an object is in use). It does not respond to release and returns false if it fails.
